      +--------------------------------.....+     +-------+------.....+
      | Options (IU)             |                | 0xFF  |
      .                          .                +-------+-----------+
      . OSCORE Option            .                |                   |
      +------+-------------------+                | Payload           |
      | 0xFF |                                    |                   |
      +------+------------+                       +-------------------+
      |  Ciphertext       |<---------\                      |
      |                   |          |                      v
      +-------------------+          |             +-----------------+
              |                      |             |   Inner SCHC    |
              v                      |             |    Instance     |
        +-----------------+          |             +-----------------+
        |   Outer SCHC    |          |                     |
        |    Instance     |          |                     v
        +-----------------+          |             +-------+
              |                      |             |RuleID |
              v                      |             +-------+-----------+
